<template>
<svg width="90" height="60" viewBox="0 0 90 60" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="empty-treemap-svg">
<rect x="15" y="15" width="60" height="30" rx="4" fill="#A0C4FF" opacity="0.25" />
<rect class="treemap-rect rect1" x="20" y="20" width="20" height="10" rx="2" />
<rect class="treemap-rect rect2" x="42" y="20" width="28" height="10" rx="2" />
<rect class="treemap-rect rect3" x="20" y="32" width="18" height="8" rx="2" />
<rect class="treemap-rect rect4" x="40" y="32" width="30" height="8" rx="2" />
</svg>
</template>

<script setup>
</script>

<style scoped>
.empty-treemap-svg {
    display: block;
    margin: 0 auto;
    animation: floatX 3.2s ease-in-out infinite;
}
.treemap-rect {
    opacity: 0.7;
    fill: #4F8EF7;
    animation: treemap-pop 1.2s cubic-bezier(.4,1.6,.6,1) infinite alternate;
}
.rect1 { animation-delay: 0.1s; fill: #A0C4FF; }
.rect2 { animation-delay: 0.3s; fill: #FFB300; }
.rect3 { animation-delay: 0.5s; fill: #A0C4FF; }
.rect4 { animation-delay: 0.7s; fill: #4F8EF7; }
@keyframes treemap-pop {
    0% { transform: scale(0.8); }
    60% { transform: scale(1.1); }
    100% { transform: scale(0.8); }
}
@keyframes floatX {
    0% { transform: translateY(0) translateX(0); }
    25% { transform: translateY(-8px) translateX(4px); }
    50% { transform: translateY(-12px) translateX(-4px); }
    75% { transform: translateY(-8px) translateX(4px); }
    100% { transform: translateY(0) translateX(0); }
}
</style>
